{"tid":427818,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"河野公平希望重賽！","createTime":"2017-10-07T16:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T16:09:02.000Z","uid":4661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac5cefc3e2525168ecb74f1188b3e61fde07c418","tid":427818,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港拳手曹星如以點數擊倒前世界冠軍的日本拳手河野公平。曹星如的經理人兼總教練劉志遠在賽後表示，非常擔心曹星如的傷勢，懷疑他的眼部出現骨折，已將他送往醫院作檢查。<br />\n<br />\n劉志遠表示，曹星如的表現有進步，比以往克制，可以形容他已經達到世界級拳手的水準。劉志遠指，曹星如於賽後有點不開心，因為覺得未能為觀眾完成合共12回合的賽事。<br />\n<br />\n劉志遠說，河野公平及他的教練都表示，希望重賽，會視乎曹星如的傷勢、康復進度及意願再作決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1357798-20171007.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1357798-20171007.htm&d=sYciqWR0qE%2Fb64lOkGl%2FAaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=0815d9f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1357798-20171007.htm&h=abd24199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1357798-20171007.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5f80ffef50f5a7dbfddcfae9075e75f44afa0530","tid":427818,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:08:07.000Z","msg":"下次要撞到你入ICU <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e143272d3f29e821ce2db28169ddf370597a0a","tid":427818,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:09:02.000Z","msg":"下次打死佢<br />\n<br />\n反正打腫佢，分數都係曹畜贏"}]}